        "title": "Mitochondrial fusion but not fission regulates larval growth and synaptic development through steroid hormone production", 
        "published": "2014-10-14T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2014-10-14T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 3, 
